Navigation Drawer Module for Mobile UI Framework

This module provides navigation drawer (side menu) system for mobile applications.
Implements slide-out navigation menus with gesture support, menu item management,
and drawer animations optimized for mobile drawer navigation patterns.

Key Features:
- Slide-out navigation drawer
- Left and right drawer support
- Gesture-based drawer opening/closing
- Menu item hierarchy and grouping
- Drawer header customization
- Overlay and push drawer modes
- Drawer state management
- Accessibility drawer navigation
- Custom drawer animations
- Drawer width and appearance control
- Integration with main content
- Platform-specific drawer styles

Provides complete drawer navigation system for building mobile applications
with side navigation menus and proper gesture interactions.
:End Note

